'''标准周刊'''（{{lang-en|The Weekly Standard}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/9/9/1/n2642773.htm|title=美著名周刊：中澳关系激情已逝|date=2009-09-01|publisher=[[大纪元时报|大纪元时报]]|access-date=2020-07-01|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323141201/https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/9/9/1/n2642773.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>），又译作'''每周标准'''<ref>{{cite book|author=陈柏安|title=部落格: 改变世界的信息革命|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eTr3sDb0ERQC&pg=RA3-PA98|year=2007|publisher=五南图书出版股份有限公司|isbn=978-957-11-4593-8|pages=3–|access-date=2020-07-01|archive-date=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708200550/https://books.google.com/books?id=eTr3sDb0ERQC&pg=RA3-PA98|dead-url=no}}</ref>、'''旗帜周刊'''<ref name="《外参》编辑部2014">{{cite book|author=《外参》编辑部|title=《外参》第54期: 围剿新“四人帮”最后一战|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fcMVBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT76|date=2014年10月16日|publisher=外参杂志社|isbn=978-1-63032-632-6|pages=76–|access-date=2020年7月1日|archive-date=2020年8月1日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801205420/https://books.google.com/books?id=fcMVBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT76|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一本[[美国|美国]]具有重要影响力的[[保守派|保守派]]政治和文化杂志<ref>Paul Farhi.{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/the-weekly-standard-influential-conservative-magazine-will-shutter/2018/12/14/051884cc-ffbb-11e8-83c0-b06139e540e5_story.html|title=The Weekly Standard, influential conservative magazine, will shutter|date=Dec 15, 2018|publisher=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|access-date=2020-07-01|archive-date=2019-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120015633/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/the-weekly-standard-influential-conservative-magazine-will-shutter/2018/12/14/051884cc-ffbb-11e8-83c0-b06139e540e5_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，集新闻、分析和评论于一体，停刊前每年出版48期。该杂志最初由[[创始人|创始人]][[比尔·克里斯托|比尔·克里斯托]]和[[弗雷德·巴恩斯|弗雷德·巴恩斯]]（Fred Barnes）[[编辑|编辑]]，以强烈的亲以色列和支持[[美伊战争|美伊战争]]的立场而闻名，被誉为“[[新保守主义|新保守主义]]的堡垒”（"redoubt of neoconservatism"<ref name="Crockett2012">{{cite book|author=Charles E. Crockett|title=A Murder of Crows: America's Raucous Right-Wing|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4_p7S4cHWVgC&pg=PA145|date=18 July 2012|publisher=Xlibris Corporation|isbn=978-1-4771-0503-0|pages=145–|access-date=2020-07-01|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713033015/https://books.google.com/books?id=4_p7S4cHWVgC&pg=PA145|dead-url=no}}</ref>）和“新保守主义的圣经”（ "the neocon bible"）<ref>{{cite news |first=Max |last=Boot |url=http://www.opinionjournal.com/editorial/feature.html?id=110002840 |title=What the Heck Is a 'Neocon'? |date=December 30, 2002 |work=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]] |quote="the Weekly Standard, ... is known as a redoubt of 'neoconservatism'" |accessdate=2020-07-01 |archive-date=2009-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090805233716/http://www.opinionjournal.com/editorial/feature.html?id=110002840 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

该杂志的创始出版商[[新闻集团_(1979－2013年)|新闻集团]]（News Corporation）于1995年9月18日首发该刊<ref>"Ten years ago, The Weekly Standard debuted, a conservative journal of opinion [f]rom Washington, D.C., edited by William Kristol". October 24, 2005. National Review]]: "The Week".</ref>。2009年，新闻集团将该杂志出售给[[安舒茨公司|安舒茨公司]]（Anschutz Corporation）的子公司<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://mediadc.com/#our-brands|title=MediaDC.com|website=MediaDC.com|language=|access-date=2020-07-01|archive-date=2021-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305151410/https://www.mediadc.com/#our-brands|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年12月14日，其所有者宣布该杂志停刊，最后一期于12月17日出版<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/12/14/business/media/weekly-standard-closing.html|title=The Weekly Standard, Pugnacious to the End, Will Cease Publication|last=Grynbaum|first=Michael M.|date=December 14, 2018|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=|last2=Rutenberg|first2=Jim|language=|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826214358/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/12/14/business/media/weekly-standard-closing.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

